{"tid":2238163,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐，泰式香葉炒肉碎飯配炸蛋","createTime":"2020-10-11T02:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T14:51:29.000Z","uid":93141,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e3a3de3e16539eef2116bf0ebc0d1ae4e0f280d5","tid":2238163,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"因為lunch食左牛排，所以夜晚就食返少少簡單又開胃既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5w9nQDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5w9nQDb.jpg&h=71084dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料: 免治豬/雞肉，蒜頭切碎，辣椒切碎，豆角切粒，金不換(九層塔)，豉油，蠔油，魚露，青檸汁，糖<br />\n<br />\n豉油，蠔油，魚露，青檸汁，糖溝到鍾意自己鍾意既酸鹹甜鮮備用<br />\n大火鑊加油，爆香蒜頭同辣椒後加肉炒<br />\n肉開始變色後加豆角繼續爆，要保持拋鑊/攪拌以防煮燶<br />\n豆角出水後加調味汁，炒到材料均勻上色<br />\n上色後熄火，離爐加金不換，撈勻就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n炸蛋做法: <br />\n<br />\n用多比平時簡單既兩倍油落pan，夠熱後打蛋後，之後唔好移動個pan<br />\n用羹淋油上未熟既蛋白到，等蛋白開始產生氣泡就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n好少煮泰式，所以一開始冇咩信心做炸蛋，點知原來咁簡單<br />\n順帶一提，好多人以為redbull係鬼佬野，其實起源係泰國，所以今次配redbull<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1914eecdf566adf83852c3204e909ecb9ee530a9","tid":2238163,"uid":93141,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"Rare image of my roommate唔識用鑊差d火燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvBtMbU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvBtMbU.png&h=4ee97c54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2aac1e0af1adfd044e481e4bd327bd5608112f9e","tid":2238163,"uid":211549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T02:28:09.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eed864a7e7c16e740cbfd4eae1dd63408bc3c93","tid":2238163,"uid":93141,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"真roommate報告: 已經全壘打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"